  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when you had to provide people for something that was not defined-- the purpose was not defined; it was called for labor-- and when the people who came for the call up-- because at first it was all very nice.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You receive an advanced notice that tomorrow you have to present yourself at a certain--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stop?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, that tomorrow, at a certain time you have to present yourself at a certain place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you probably have heard the expression [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when you saw who is coming to the places, you had no illusions that this is not for work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were the old, and the sick, the infirms, the abandoned children, the children from orphanage, mothers with children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And although it was sane mind, there were no illusions to a mind of of any Jew.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The picture was not clear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not clear.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the urge and the desire to leave was such that it obscured all logic--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
